org.jamsim.ascape.stats
Class StatsFunctionRow<T>

java.lang.Object
  org.jamsim.ascape.stats.StatsFunctionRow<T>
Type Parameters:
T - scape member
public class StatsFunctionRow<T>
extends Object

A stats row representing a function and a mutable denominator value. Can be combined with a predicate to produce a CollectorFunction via a call to getCollectorFunction(StatsPredicate, Scape).
